docs.text: There is one supported way to get started with RBXLuaAPI. Method 1: Command Line ¶ Copy and paste this command into the command line: git clone https://github.com/polycue/rbxlua-api.git cd rbxlua-api rojo build -o RBXLuaAPI.rbxmx move RBXLuaAPI.rbxmx .. del /f /s /q *.* cd .. rmdir /s /q rbxlua-api
